{"tid":2507894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"月薪料達10萬 新任民政事務局政治助理張進樂自稱工作係「行行企企」：行多啲自然知要做咩","createTime":"2021-04-28T10:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T11:39:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7d055922c1e80f8efe896b434bbfacd6db04ac2c","tid":2507894,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:29:24.000Z","msg":"新任民政事務局政治助理、民建聯成員張進樂，未上任就被傳媒指佢同民政局長徐英偉有過合作關係。今日張進樂現身立法會時嗰陣就同記者講，自己嘅工作就係「行行企企」，總之行多啲就自然會知道有咩要做。<br />\n<br />\n政府喺3月30日宣佈，年僅29歲嘅張進樂係代替今年初跳船嘅黎穎瑜，接任做民政局政助，月薪估計介乎7.5萬至10.5萬。上任前佢已經被指同徐英偉份屬黨友外，做政助前已經係徐英偉下屬，而家仲升呢做政助。<br />\n<br />\n張進樂就話，佢之前除咗同徐英偉一齊出席過廿幾場「完善」選舉制度嘅解說會外，仲話原來徐英偉有提點佢，做政助得閒要多啲落立法會、喺走廊「行行企企」， 總之喺走廊多啲行吓，就會自自然然知道要做啲咩喎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210428/65VLLGJPYBBALNRUFZSKE3OLZE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210428%2F65VLLGJPYBBALNRUFZSKE3OLZE%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0mCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=1696fe69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210428%2F65VLLGJPYBBALNRUFZSKE3OLZE%2F&h=7efa533e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210428/65VLLGJPYBBALNRUFZSKE3OLZE/</a>"},{"pid":"edbbedda7d8505d3527417a3b2c24c32dd9fd217","tid":2507894,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8904bf3c9d93b0803b4bfe95946edbb82ffb2fd1","tid":2507894,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:30:26.000Z","msg":"正宗賊樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cc57f43ffc90f402c1ddc5180eaa71ab5ebc06","tid":2507894,"uid":280593,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:31:49.000Z"